snippet.title: Preview of WTC : Recruitment Day
snippet.description:
This is a short preview of an upcoming episode in the WTC series, and is partially voice by the lovely Sarah (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC-sgoGc0NRWaInefBin6Wbw/featured) as the voice of  Grendel Jinx.

Various sound effects still need to be added, as well as the remaining voice files, but it is nearly complete.

#vn #visualnovel #wtc #comedy #drama #wtcrd #va #anime
